For changing available positions
1. Open "jobopenings.yml"
2. Without changing the format or indentation, change the information after the colons and asterisks.
3. If there is more than one position available, copy the whole section from "-title" to "keywords", making sure the indentation is the same. Edit accordingly 
4. Test changes on local host
5. Revise accordingly.
6. Save changes.

If there are no available positions:
1. Open jobopenings.yml
2. Convert all to comment (highlight all > edit > Toggle comment)
Notes: Relevant pages are careers.md (intro text) , careers.html (infrastructure for each job opening), and jobopenings.yml (content for each job opening). 